dct_description_sm: In lower margin: "Survey of Palestine, Jaffa 1937. Ordnance Survey, 1938." Ancillary map: Southern Palestine. Scale 1:200,000. Note: "Numbers in hatched areas indicate percentage of land held by Jews." Jewish land holdings 1938, Scale 1:750,000, Ordnance Survey
